.autorize-block-wrap
	.autorize-block#login
		h1.autorize-block__head Авторизуйтесь
		form.autorize-block__form
			.autorize-block__data.autorize-block__login
				input(type="text" placeholder="Логин").autorize-block__input-text
			.autorize-block__data.autorize-block__password
				input(type="text" placeholder="Пароль").autorize-block__input-text
			.autorize-block__data.autorize-block__check
				input(type="checkbox" id="check").hidden
				label(for="check") Я человек
			.autorize-block__data.autorize-block__check-again
				.autorize-block__text Вы точно не робот?
				.autorize-block__choice1
					input(type="radio" id="answer1" name="yes")
					label(for="answer1") Да
				.autorize-block__choice2
					input(type="radio" id="answer2" name="no")
					label(for="answer2") Не уверен
		.autorize-block__enter Вернуться или войти?
			ul.autorize-block__enter-list
				li.autorize-block__enter-item.autorize-block__enter-item_first
					a(href="#").autorize-block__enter-link На главную
				li.autorize-block__enter-item
					a(href="#").autorize-block__enter-link Войти
			